headline: AIG Deepens Ties To Convex And Onex To Shape Earnings Mix
summary: American International Group (NYSE:AIG) has completed minority equity investments in Convex Group and Onex Corporation. The transactions include a multi year quota share reinsurance arrangement with Convex Group. AIG plans to have a director serve on Onex Corporation’s board. AIG has committed US$2b to funds managed by Onex.
